EarthLink

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


EarthLink Holding Corp.





Part of the EarthLink headquarters in Atlanta.




Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: ELNK


Industry
Managed network and cloud services provider, and ISP


Founded
1994


Founders
Sky Dayton, Reed Slatkin[1][2]


Headquarters
Atlanta, Georgia



Key people


Joseph F. Eazor (CEO)



